body:
http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/site/guide/champions.html
Why is it that NA gets champions like Jinx Khazix and Lux while oce get weak, rarely played champions like miss fortune as the starting champions?

replies.body:
Are they? I hadn't noticed...
Thought everyone got the same free week champs no matter what region.

Because level 1 - 5 players don't really care because it takes quite a bit more skill to take advantage of the small power gaps between meta and non meta champions?

I've never heard a person create an account and say "AWWW I wanted Darius, not Alistair!" with only 2 games and no experience in either champ.
because oce is not as good as other regions. Oce is trash
